                  <provenance>
                     <persName ref="PRS5882KasaSeb" role="donor">šum ʾagāme Kāsā</persName> (Walda ʾAragāwi) is mentioned
                     as the donor in Additio 1, with his father Walda Kidān (<persName ref="PRS8668SebhatA">
                        <roleName type="title">rās</roleName> Sǝbḥāt ʾAragāwi</persName>)
                     and his mother Walatta Yoḥannǝs. The names are also mentioned in the
                     supplication formulas, Walda ʾAragāwi throughout the Ms., Walda Kidān (e.g.,
                     <locus target="#102vc">102vc</locus>, 139rc, 140vc), and Walatta Yoḥannǝs
                     (e.g., <locus target="#76vb">76vb</locus>, 132rc).</provenance>
